.php/2025/06/24/kingdom-of-days-june-24-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 32954, "position": 4}, "title": "June 24", "author": "Ken", "date": "June 24, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "Patti Scialfa tries out for the E Street Band, Bruce plays host to a ton of guests for a special Concert to Fight Hunger, and much more on this eventful date in Springsteen history.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/bba.png?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/bba.png?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/bba.png?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/bba.png?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/bba.png?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 3490, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/1987/03/19/meeting-across-the-river-bruce-springsteen-and-the-asbury-park-all-star-revue-got-to-get-you-off-my-mind/", "url_meta": {"origin": 32954, "position": 5}, "title": "Got to Get You Off My Mind", "author": "Ken", "date": "March 19, 1987", "format": false, "excerpt": "When Southside Johnny took ill, Bruce, Steve, the E Street Band, and the Jukes came to the rescue. From May 1977, here's one of Bruce's only performances of the Solomon Burke classic.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Cover Me&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Cover Me", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/cover-me/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/admin-ajax-2026-06-09